    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (0.89 / (wp.abs(v2 + 0.30) * wp.sin(v1 + 0.54)))
    v0 = wp.exp((0.59 / (v1 + 0.98 * tmp + 0.42)))
    tmp = ((wp.exp(v2 + 0.49) + v1) / wp.sin(v0))
    v0 = (((v2 + 0.36 * v0 + 0.34) - wp.cos(v0 + 0.71)) / v0)
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.cos(v2 + 0.68)) - (wp.exp(tmp + 0.12) + (v1 + 0.68 * v2 + 0.28)))
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v1 + 0.82)) + (wp.exp(tmp + 0.68) * wp.cos(v1 + 0.83)))
    data[tid] = v0
